headline.print_headline: Tesco Takes on UK Banks With Current Account Launch
headline.main: Tesco Takes on UK Banks With Current Account Launch

lead_paragraph: Tesco Bank, the financial services arm of Britain's biggest retailer, has launched its first personal current or checking account, looking to challenge established lenders and bring shoppers back into its parent's stores.
